name: Wrap
description:
Hand dyed wraps for swaddling babies 

These are all hand made and each one is different from the one before.  You can also choose from a circle or stripe design.

They make an excellent present.

Wraps are made with Muslin (for warmer months) or Flannelette  (for colder months).  Both fabrics are suitable for babies with sensitive skin types.

Machine washable in both hot and cold water.   Colours are long lasting and will stay vibrant regardless of frequent washing.
